text: Ellen Katherine Pompeo (November 10, 1969) is an American actress. She works mostly in television shows. She portrayed the character Meredith Grey in Grey's Anatomy. She also does other television work. She was born in Everett, Massachusetts. She married producer Chris Ivery in 2007. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:1969 births Category:Living people category:Actors from Massachusetts
